snippet.title: Fall Guys - Season 5 - Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Get ready to stumble in the jungle! Fall Guys: Ultimate Knockout Season 5 is tumbling out on July 20th, fully-equipped with an adventurous theme featuring giant swinging logs, a mysterious Lost Temple and...mechanical Rhinos?!

www.fallguys.com
